[09:13:37 DBG] Compiling query expression: 
'DbSet<ToDoList>()
    .Include(x => x.Items)
    .SingleOrDefault(l => l.Id == __toDoListId_0)'
[09:13:37 DBG] Including navigation: 'ToDoList.Items'.
[09:13:37 DBG] Generated query execution expression: 
'queryContext => new SingleQueryingEnumerable<ToDoList>(
    (RelationalQueryContext)queryContext, 
    RelationalCommandCache.SelectExpression(
        Projection Mapping:
        SELECT t.Id, t.Position, t.Reminded, t.ReminderDate, t.Title, i.Id, i.Description, i.IsCompleted, i.Position, i.ToDoListId
        FROM Projection Mapping:
        (
            SELECT TOP(2) l.Id, l.Position, l.Reminded, l.ReminderDate, l.Title
            FROM Lists AS l
            WHERE l.Id == @__toDoListId_0
        ) AS t
        LEFT JOIN Items AS i ON t.Id == i.ToDoListId
        ORDER BY t.Id ASC, i.Id ASC), 
    Func<QueryContext, DbDataReader, ResultContext, SingleQueryResultCoordinator, ToDoList>, 
    ToDoInfrastructure.ToDoDbContext, 
    False, 
    False
)
    .SingleOrDefault()'
